-- Nigeria's 2024 bond to be added to JP Morgan bond index on Aug. 29
-- By Chijioke Ohuocha
-- Thu Aug 21, 2014 11:19AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, Aug 21 (Reuters) - Nigeria's 2024 bond will be included in JP Morgan's Government Bond Index-Emerging Markets (GBI-EM) on August 29, in addition to three other bonds already listed, a JP Morgan internal document released on Thursday showed.

